            <h1>Major Works</h1>
            <p>Julio Iglesias has a number of hit albums that are all time favourites. Most popular of them are 
            ‘El Amor’ (1975), ‘Julio’ (1983), ‘1100 Bel Air Place’ (1984), ‘Un Hombre Solo’ (1987), ‘My Life: The Greatest Hits’ (1998),
             ‘Divorcio’ (2003) and ‘Romantic Classics’ (2006).</p>
